 Homemade aioli complements many different flavours.","If your aioli has not thickened after step 4, mix for a further <strong>2 min\/speed 4<\/strong><strong> <\/strong>or until a mayonnaise consistency is achieved.","<strong>Garlic aioli<\/strong>: omit the lemon zest and capers. Add 1- 2 extra garlic cloves to taste in step 1 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Lemon aioli<\/strong>: omit the capers. Add an extra 1 - 2 pieces of lemon zest (5 x 2 cm) to taste in step 1 and proceed as per recipe.","<strong>Citrus aioli<\/strong>: omit the capers and use a combination of orange, lemon and lime zest pieces (5 x 2 cm) in stp 1 to create your flavour of choice. Proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","15m","1 total recipe"]}